                    <h1 itemprop="name"><a class="article-title" href="/post/25-09-23-pac-dimmer/">230V Phase Angle Control Dimmer</a></h1>
                </header>
                
                <div class="article-meta">
                    <a href="/post/25-09-23-pac-dimmer/" class="article-date">
                        <time datetime='2023-09-25T22:29:37.000&#43;02:00' itemprop="datePublished">2023-09-25</time>
                    </a>
                    
                    
                    
                </div>
                <div class="article-entry" itemprop="articleBody">
                    <p>
                        <a class="article-title" href="/post/25-09-23-pac-dimmer/"><img width=1000 height=100 alt="Banner" src="/post/25-09-23-pac-dimmer//banner.jpg"></a><br>
                    A fairly simple phase angle control dimmer using a triac, diac, resistor, potentiometer and a capacitor. For noise suppression I added an inductor and a filter capacitor.
                    </p>
                    <p class="article-more-link">
                        <a href="/post/25-09-23-pac-dimmer/">Read More</a>
                    </p>
